title: Software Engineer
about:
I'm a software engineer with three years of experience in the industry. I graduated with a master's degree in Computer Science (Scientists and Engineers) from the University of Southern California in December 2023.
Prior to completing my master's degree, I worked as a full stack developer at Accenture in India, with a focus on ASP .NET web applications.
